  "last_post_content": "\ud83d\udee0\ufe0f How teams solved it.\nIndustry leaders reveal what works (and what doesn't).\n\n\ud83d\udd0d Breakdown: Building in the Agentic Era with Power BI and Fabric\n\n\ud83d\udcca Data: Microsoft Build 2026 marks a major shift in how developers build data experiences with AI agents. Today we're announcing two capabilities that bring agentic analytics to the...\n\ud83c\udfaf Impact: practical signal for building reliable systems.\n\nHow to apply this:\n\u2192 Step 1: Feature flags decouple deployment risk from feature risk\n\u2192 Step 2: Progressive delivery beats blue-green for complex systems\n\u2192 Step 3: Measure impact and iterate based on results\n\nWhat CI/CD bottleneck slows your team down most?\n\n#Looker #Insights #Automation #DataWarehouse #Qlik #SSIS #AdvancedAnalytics\n\n\u2753 How would you adapt this for your team?\n\n\ud83e\udd1d Join the discussion: https://community.fabric.microsoft.com/t5/Power-BI-Updates-Blog/Building-in-the-Agentic-Era-with-Power-BI-and-Fabric/ba-p/5190754\n\n#PowerBI #BusinessIntelligence #DataAnalytics #MySQL #SSAS #Oracle #SSRS",
